title: Does Meme Accurately Compare US COVID Relief Funds to Other Countries’?
subtitle: Comparing apples to oranges is ironically a fruitless method of argument.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: A meme accurately shows how countries including Australia, Canada, Denmark, France, Germany, Ireland, U.K., and the U.S. are providing stimulus relief funds to their economies reeling from the COVID-19 pandemic.
